  "1710740": {
    "name": "Dungeon Full Dive: Game Master Edition",
    "steam_appid": 1710740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/9580b85b012b0bbf65dfde96484db207.poster.avif?t=1753962939\" width=600 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/9580b85b012b0bbf65dfde96484db207.webm?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/9580b85b012b0bbf65dfde96484db207.mp4?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将您的桌上冒险提升到新的水平</h2><br>&quot;DFD：游戏大师版&quot;是在线玩桌上角色扮演游戏(TTRPGs)的最佳方式。为游戏大师和追求极致灵活性、创造力及沉浸感的玩家设计。这个版本解锁了您冒险的全部潜力。<br><br>&quot;Dungeon Full Dive：游戏大师版&quot;的特点：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>主持无限制的游戏会话：</strong>GM版允许您主持尽可能多的TTRPG会话。与朋友或在线上遇到的新人一起玩。<br></li><li><strong>独家GM版骰子：</strong>通过一个独家骰子套装为您所有的TTRPG会话增添新的个性层次，为您的投掷增添无与伦比的风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/d70b6ae9430a2ac18d74504bd34e045e.avif?t=1753962939\" width=616 height=278 /></span><br></li><li><strong>完全访问GM工具：</strong>在在线游戏中利用DFD的游戏大师工具全套。从沉浸式声音板到动态天气系统，这些工具被精心制作，旨在将您的故事讲述提升到一个新的水平！<br></li><li><strong>无限制的角色创建：</strong>无限制地制作和定制角色。GM版将可用的角色槽位从3个提升到无限。<br></li><li><strong>无限制的地图建造能力：</strong>无限制地构建和定制世界。GM版将可用的地图槽位从2个提升到无限。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/f4d344256e137428aee9c2052846064a.avif?t=1753962939\" width=621 height=66 /></span><br>无论是使用鼠标和键盘还是在虚拟现实中，都可以与朋友一起探险，或者与随机的旅行者建立一个全新的派对。当然，PC 和 VR 之间支持跨平台功能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/aac54bcb4094396be5410c2b85fdbf84.poster.avif?t=1753962939\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/aac54bcb4094396be5410c2b85fdbf84.webm?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/aac54bcb4094396be5410c2b85fdbf84.mp4?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>任何 TRPG 游戏都可以玩。在游戏中创建、修改你的玩家角色卡等等。DFD 还包括 DnD 5e 的游戏机制和能力值集成。跟踪主动这样的事情只需点个按就可以！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/508bccad985f5f862df08df9e23dcf55.poster.avif?t=1753962939\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/508bccad985f5f862df08df9e23dcf55.webm?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/508bccad985f5f862df08df9e23dcf55.mp4?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>放置玩家角色和怪物，然后切换到他们的角度、从他们的眼睛里体验。这是有史以来第一次在你梦想中的桌面冒险探险：在酒馆喝一杯，在城市广场演奏一首歌，在黑暗的森林去探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/186e3795491b4747a1d77dc513e1f64c.poster.avif?t=1753962939\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/186e3795491b4747a1d77dc513e1f64c.webm?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/186e3795491b4747a1d77dc513e1f64c.mp4?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作战地图是你自己可以选择，调整，甚至创建的。DFD 提供各种各样的精心制作的 3D 地图。使用提供的地图、或使用地图编辑器对其进行修改、或白手起家地创建自己的地图！选择战斗地点，无论是在冰冷的深山还是在地下洞穴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/b4653617941a90df2d6904a01f4bcb1d.poster.avif?t=1753962939\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/b4653617941a90df2d6904a01f4bcb1d.webm?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710740/extras/b4653617941a90df2d6904a01f4bcb1d.mp4?t=1753962939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用 DFD 强大的玩家角色编辑器构建一支大军！创造你的英雄，并使用 DFD 的角色定制系统使他们独一无二：你想成为任何人就成为任何人。",
